    <img class="picture pull-right img-responsive" itemprop="image" data-fieldname="picture" src="/media/cache/e3/e0/e3e097f1afa8e016e76a51938c5834ae.jpg" width="400" height="153" data-src="/static/img/events/nlff_logo.png" data-width="470" data-height="180" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#img-picture-605" alt="" data-bind="attr: { src: pictureData().displaySrc, width: pictureData().displayWidth, height: pictureData().displayHeight, 'data-src': pictureData().src, 'data-width': pictureData().width, 'data-height': pictureData().height }" /><div class="modal " id="img-picture-605">    <div class="modal-dialog">        <div class="modal-content">            <div class="modal-header">                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">                    &times;                </button>            </div>            <div class="modal-body">                <img src="/static/img/events/nlff_logo.png" class="img-responsive" alt="" data-bind="attr: {src: pictureData().displaySrc}">            </div>        </div>    </div></div>

    <h3><time class="startDate" datetime="2010-03-20" data-bind="attr:{datetime:startDateTime()},text:displayStart()">Saturday 20</time> to <time class="endDate" datetime="2010-03-27" data-bind="attr:{datetime:endDateTime()},text:displayEnd()">Saturday 27 March 2010</time></h3>

    <meta itemprop="image" content="/media/cache/e3/e0/e3e097f1afa8e016e76a51938c5834ae.jpg">

    <div class="bodysection">
        <div class="body" itemprop="about" data-fieldname="body" data-bind="htmlValue:body"><p>Northern Lights Film Festival is in it's 7th year.</p>
<p>The Northern Lights Film Festival asked partners across the region and  beyond to put together programmes and events that celebrate people who  are taking risks, playing new games and setting their own rules.</p></div>
    </div>

    </div>

