                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/558">Involuntary (2008)</a></h1>

                <h2>24 Mar 2010, 7:30 a.m.</h2>

                <p>A preview of a great new film from Sweden, It has received massive acclaim at festivals around the world and is brought to the North East ahead of it's UK distribution later this year by Star and Shadow and Northern Lights Film Festival.</p>

